Description: Knowledge graph and semantic search engine for Jetson AI
 Brain Server is a high-performance knowledge management system designed
 for the Jetson Nano platform. It provides semantic search capabilities
 using 384-dimensional embeddings and a knowledge graph with entity
 relationship extraction.
 .
 Key features:
 .
  - Semantic search with model2vec-rs (minishlab/potion-retrieval-32M)
  - Knowledge graph with entity/relationship extraction
  - SQLite database with connection pooling (r2d2)
  - RESTful API endpoints for search, ingestion, and graph traversal
  - Optimized for ARM64 Cortex-A57 processors
  - Production-ready with systemd integration
 .
 This package includes the brain-server binary and systemd service file.
 Configuration files are installed to /etc/brain-server/ and data files
 to /var/lib/brain-server/.
